{
  "updated_summary": "A woman with long dark hair styled in two braids, wearing a black 'white fox' top, begins by stating her intention to clean, initiating a montage of tidying a cluttered room where she sorts Scattered Clothes into a Cardboard Box amidst rustling sounds. She then moves to a white Closet, revealing neat organization, and proceeds to clean a white Vanity area with audible wiping sounds, noting on-screen text about the vanity needing work. Transitioning to her laundry area, she places white New Balance sneakers into a Samsung washing machine, adding ECOS detergent with a pouring sound, intending to clean them based on advice. Later, in a bright kitchen, she holds fresh rosemary, discussing her goal to make rosemary water for hair growth in 2024. She then prepares a rosemary concoction in a black speckled saucepan on a gas stove, explaining the process of boiling and steeping the rosemary for a potent hair spray. Shifting topics, she mentions an upcoming grocery trip for health items to boost immunity due to widespread illness. She then plans to make ginger turmeric lemon orange shots, having ordered shot glasses, and notes the gloomy, rainy weather makes motivation difficult. Driving in her car, she lists ingredients for health shots and shows her smartphone's grocery list app, finding the rainy grocery shopping "cozy" and expressing a desire for a white Christmas. At the grocery store, she selects milk, sweet potatoes, greens, chicken thighs, and organic eggs, later unpacking her haul at a white table, highlighting popping corn for Joel, rice stick noodles, ginger, turmeric, Zevia Ginger Root Beer, organic potatoes, bone broth, and eggnog. She then details her grocery purchases, including Dew Fresh Honey due to rain, organic garlic powder, rosemary for hair, avocados, limes, oranges, apples, parsley, and yams, noting the dark, rainy day necessitates turning on house lights. Finally, she expresses a strong aversion to a dirty fridge, emphasizing the need to clean it before putting away fresh groceries, and proceeds to organize the refrigerator in her modern kitchen, accompanied by chill lo-fi music and the sounds of items being moved."
}
